3 SUMMARY
44 This bill amends Resolve 2025, chapter 108, which established the Real Estate Property
55 Tax Relief Task Force, to allow the task force to meet 8 times in 2026. For tax years
66 beginning on or after January 1, 2026, the bill increases from $1,000 to $1,500 the property
77 tax fairness credit for individuals under 65 years of age. The bill also requires the
88 Department of Administrative and Financial Services, Bureau of Revenue Services to
99 administer a survey to assessors to gather data on the administration of the Maine Tree
1100 Growth Tax Law.
